Get Predictions and Improvements with Einstein Prediction Service
The Einstein Prediction Service REST API enables you to run predictions, manage prediction definitions, and manage models.
REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS:
View Einstein Discovery Recommendations
Deploy the model you want to use for predictions. For instructions, see Deploy a Model.
Use your favorite REST client. You must have a connected app that handles Salesforce authentication for your REST client.
Interact With Einstein Prediction Service
Learn how to access Einstein Discovery features programmatically using the Einstein Discovery REST API Developer Guide.
Review REST API considerations and use cases in the Examples section.
Discover available API endpoints in the Resources section.
